data.description: The waterfront three-bedroom, two-bathroom conch cottage in the Lower Keys now comes with a fantastic PRICE REDUCTION down to $775,000. Additionally, the sellers are providing a generous $10,000 credit, earmarked specifically for a new roof. This not only enhances the property's value but also reduces wind insurance costs. To add even more flexibility, the sellers are open to a 2/1 Buy Down.Nestled along a premier canal network, this charming cottage boasts a concrete seawall on a deep draft canal system, ensuring quick access to the open waters within a mere 10 minutes. For added privacy and security, the property is enclosed by a fence and features a gate.The spacious yard offers ample room for a pool or the creation of a lush tropical garden.Constructed with resilient materials like concrete, a metal roof, and impact windows, this home is built to withstand the test of time.Step inside to discover a cozy Key West ambiance with soft gray tones, bead board, and tile floors. The kitchen has undergone recent updates, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a subway tile backsplash, and new cabinets - a dream for any home chef.Conveniently located near shopping and restaurants, this property also includes a 5000-pound boat lift, adding an extra layer of appeal.Important documents such as the survey and EC are available for your reference.
